UserComments.Comment: Just like on Westbahnhof, most of the charge points are out of order, and have been broken for a long time. Only two Type 2 cars can charge at any given time. To make matters worse, several hybrid drivers "charge" their cars during the day for 8 hours or more. That is, if the nearby car wash doesn't block the charger points with their customer cars. If you arrive after 19:00 in the evening, you're fine. Charging before then is a matter of luck.
